Writes one byte directly to outputStream. Can be used to send customized * commands to printer.

Write some usual ESC/POS commands to the OutPutStream.

* ESC/POS was developed by Seiko Epson Corporation

* Most receipt printers on the market recognize these commands.

* and can be used to print texts, barcodes or images
delay delay in milliseconds before task is to be executed.
on if task was already scheduled or * cancelled, timer was cancelled, or timer thread terminated.
